    <div class="mb-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-foundationprimarygreen mb-4">About Taw Ha Zin Nurain Foundation</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Dedicated to education, da'wah, and total human welfare, we are a non-political, non-profit, government-registered organization serving the Ummah and beyond.</p>
